dc_title_s: Bus Routes City of Wausau, WI 2016
dc_description_s: This data layer represents bus routes for the city of Wausau, WI in 2016.
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.For complete metadata documentation, please visit https://www.marathoncounty.gov/services/property-land-information/gis-maps/explore-gis-data .
